## Superstitions

### Evil Eye
- Strangers from faraway places who make eye contact with you will inflict bad luck
	- Popular in agricultural communities where everyone knows everybody
- Can be protected against by charms


### The magic of words
- Curse scrolls
	- Writing a curse down on paper *guarantees* it to work
	- Bonus points for hiding it in their house
- Runic enchantments
